&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for experienced Critical Care Registered Nurses to join our Nurse bank. In return we offer an enhanced rate of pay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Critical Care Unit in Sherwood Forest Hospitals is looking for enthusiastic, highly motivated registered nurses. We are a 13 bedded unit who play an active role both in the Trust and the East-Midlands Critical Care Network.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Critical Care is a dynamic work environment and is constantly changing hence we are looking for nurses who will adapt to the environment and the challenges it presents.&lt;/p&gt;
